@startuml
object Teacher
object DiscordOAuthCallback
object ClassDiscordController
object GetDiscordBotInviteLinkUseCase
object BindClassDiscordGuildUseCase
object ClassroomDiscordWriter
object DiscordCacheStore
object DiscordUserGuilds <<database>>
object DiscordGuildChannels <<database>>
object ClassDiscordBindings <<database>>
Teacher --> ClassDiscordController : 1: request bot invite
ClassDiscordController --> GetDiscordBotInviteLinkUseCase : 2: build install URL
GetDiscordBotInviteLinkUseCase --> ClassroomDiscordWriter : 3: load teacher Discord user id
ClassDiscordController --> Teacher : 4: invite_link
DiscordOAuthCallback --> ClassDiscordController : 5: guild_id callback
ClassDiscordController --> DiscordCacheStore : 6: save raw guild id
DiscordCacheStore --> DiscordUserGuilds : 7: INSERT/UPDATE synced_at=null
Teacher --> ClassDiscordController : 8: select guild/channels
ClassDiscordController --> BindClassDiscordGuildUseCase : 9: execute
BindClassDiscordGuildUseCase --> ClassroomDiscordWriter : 10: validate cached guild/channels
ClassroomDiscordWriter --> DiscordGuildChannels : 11: SELECT
ClassroomDiscordWriter --> ClassDiscordBindings : 12: INSERT/UPDATE binding
@enduml
